[[File:LilHammerheadKotOR13.jpg|thumb|Hammerhead starship]]
The '''Hammerhead starship''' was a class of ship used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] during the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. In [[3963 BBY]], at least two of them were present in the Republic fleet that gathered over [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]], and one of them was seen at [[Camp Three (Serroco)|Camp Three]] on the planet [[Serroco]], shortly before the [[Battle of Serroco]].

==Behind the scenes==
The size and function of the Hammerhead starship is not made clear in its appearances. While the ship is evidently smaller than the similarly-designed [[Hammerhead-class cruiser|''Hammerhead''-class cruiser]]. It appears to be of a similar size to a [[Republic shuttle (Mandalorian Wars)|Republic shuttle variant]] used during the Mandalorian Wars, and can be seen in a landed position on [[Serroco]], with several individuals entering.

